title: For Sale:  Scam Alert !!!!! (Lot of scammers) help protect yourself  ( few helpful tips )
postcontent: (Scam Alert !!!!)Over the past few weeks I've seen tons and tons of Scammers or fake adds! Few tips: 1. - Don't message anyone that says (Washington/Washington) or (Seattle/Seattle)99% of those are out of state scams. 2. - Don't do anything through Paypal or Westermunion ! PayPal (Will Not Refund) any of your money for any gun Related item.. 3. - If someone messages asking you Location and then replies with Spokane or out of state block them.. Scam! 4. - If you meet at FFL and guy says his (Gf) will transfer the gun in her name. Probably a straw purchase! Don't do it. Not worth it 5. - If the deal is more then 30miles.. Think because a lot of people are now baiting you to come with a good deal.. but end up flaking & yes it happened to me.. 6. - Check the gun over before buying! Meet (Inside of a gunshop!) Not outside, get the gunshop owners advice and let him look it over! Could save you from headaches.7. - If the deal is to good to be true it probably is.. $1400 gun for $700 probably stolen, broken or a scam.. 8. - 99% of FN SCAR 16/17s posts are fake!! If the price is under $2300 for 16s fake.. $2650 or under for 17s Fake!! $1200-$1900 are Scams !! Hope you got some good Intel from this  briefing , Stay safe and shoot straight!2nd amendment: A well regulated Militia, being necessary to the security of a free State, the right of the people to keep and bear Arms, shall not be infringed.God bless America , The military & Police !
